Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:07.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,3... 3... 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:10.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've been studying real hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No one understands...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:16.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The exam is coming, so do a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:19.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Put in a few more runs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:22.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sing a little louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:26.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:29.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Brighten up, Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:30.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:32.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay getting all 3's.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:35.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dad used to get all 3's too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:38.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're on the right track to mediocrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:42.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Being mediocre is a personality too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:45.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you have nothing better to say, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're here because we have something we want you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:51.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:53.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Take the champon to Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:01.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know, maybe now's a good time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:05.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to make food for some outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.49,0:01:08.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, I can tell him to cook his own food.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:14.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Taking care of Sensei has become a fulfilling part of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:20.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I have a son who no longer needs my care,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:24.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and a washed-up husband who only speaks well of the food I make.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:27.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Within my bland life, Sensei is the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:32.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,that brings out the motherly love and womanliness inside of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:10.95,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Yakamashika"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:10.95,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,76)}"Translation: Noisy"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:14.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a week since I came to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:18.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't write anything that agrees with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:20.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That was just something\NI drew out of inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:20.46,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,44)}"Ease, Comfort, Relief"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:24.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:28.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to immerse myself in calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:31.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,To make that geezer eat his words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:33.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:41.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You again! Why are you here every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:45.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Because Naru is Sensei's commuter wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:47.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world did you pick that up from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa-{\i1}nee{\i0} and Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so he's the rumored guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:55.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've seen someone wear styled summer clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since we came to the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who said you could come in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The poster's been peeled off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The CDs are gone too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:07.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why did you come here all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who came here all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This used to be our base!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, where's our stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you threw it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:19.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the stuff that was here when I came, it's in that box over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,These were precious to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:28.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know... this place isn't your base anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Don't put that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're not planning on leaving here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Leave! There's a resident here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, cut us some slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:42.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're happy you get to tangle with us young gals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make it sound lewd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... It must be you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:51.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you teach this kid street slang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:54.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That wife there is the "queen" of Kabuki-cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:57.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's nice, so I'll go and have a "pillow talk"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:01.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This miso soup is some "serious juice"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I can't do nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:09.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You were listening to us and learned it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. You taught me nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you better watch out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:18.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kids her age can remember words like a mynah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:21.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm telling you your words...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Eth-Emu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:25.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I drew this for work...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, an SM club?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:37.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Eth-Emu! Eth-Emu! Eth-Emu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.44,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Ethnic Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.44,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}Emupamusa"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:40.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sign for a restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:43.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing using my tools?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:49.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.08,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Loser"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Write nicer words than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, you're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I should've figured. You did want to be a manga writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring up the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It may be better than Sensei's!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:05.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I guess it's easy being a calligrapher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:13.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look! This is the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but it's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't calligraphy one of our summer homework subjects?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have Sensei teach us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:24.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:27.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If we learn from Sensei, we'll have a shot at the gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:30.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So please help us, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we'll come again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:36.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:43.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What did I do there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And these emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:48.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...become the salve to the woman in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:51.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right! I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hina's here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:04.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to play now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:08.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Go and play outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, focus... Focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:23.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I ignore them, they'll probably leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:28.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Losty-losty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:46.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Zho... fvun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,SM...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:51.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:53.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You girls, just stay away today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:55.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Phooey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:02.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not good. My head's starting to spin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dang...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:07.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For her age, I can't believe\NMom's hooked on such a loafer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:10.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Calligraphers are just a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:14.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna give it to him straight that we can't be fixin' his meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:21.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're there, right?! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Answer the damn door right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:36.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:45.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi! What'd you do to Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What should Naru do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Hold the champon!\N--Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:56.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, lend me a bit of your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:59.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I said "champon"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing it's wrapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:11.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... But it looks terrible now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:15.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, why is he like half-dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:17.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's always like this around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:20.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Something 'bout writing words to send to a tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So he's doing an all-nighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:26.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm like this before tests too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:29.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, between a talent like him and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...the meaning of an all-nighter's gonna be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi, what's "talent"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It means there's some who can make do with little effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:41.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and others who can't do anything no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:44.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is getting all 3's the best for Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who'd you get that from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru wants to do better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd you hear it from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:56.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I won't lose doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:58.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I hid it in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:06.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't go rummaging in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:12.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It should be in that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:19.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei says that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:23.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...he can't write anything good even after writing all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:26.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei doesn't have talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:28.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,so writing all this isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:28.69,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Zenith"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:32.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru thinks Sensei is super.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This "talent" thing is so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:38.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This should be enough studying already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You dyed your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:42.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm gonna go with this from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:45.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're so half-baked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Half-baked...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:53.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's why I'm like all 3's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:55.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:59.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru... Sensei does have talent after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:02.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? You know, Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well... not that I understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You faked that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:13.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess his effort is his number-one talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:17.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hiroshi, are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:22.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You're a grown-up, and still crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:29.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:34.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Cicada shells!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's Naru's talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:42.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can gather more of these than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is "talent," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:49.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're giving it all you've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:51.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...I guess that's talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:56.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're the Village Leader's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to be bothering you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:00.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last meal we're going to bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:06.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mom doesn't say it, but I think she's burdened by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:10.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It was a burden...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:15.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And... I'm thinking of seriously studying for my exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to follow Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:20.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...and try my very best starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:23.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I liked your mom's potato stew,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:25.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening to what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:35.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right... I'll make potato stew and bring it for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's not what I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:41.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd feel bad if that champon was the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have to cook starting tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:51.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sensei, you know how to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:52.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll make curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:54.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! I'm here to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:05.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?! Am-Am-Ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:11.38,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Nanatsudake Hospital"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:15.66,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Handa Sei
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:15.66,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,73)}Private Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:16.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Heatstroke, lack of sleep, loss of appetite...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check you in for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:23.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My, Sensei, you should have told us you weren't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:26.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I wasn't getting much sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:29.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei? You going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:32.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm taking drips now, so I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:35.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... Does it hurt more than getting poked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:39.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:43.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, we'll go and get the things you'll need for the stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything, feel free to tell Iku-{\i1}chan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:52.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This nurse here's young, but already married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You better not lay a finger on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:03.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that injections hurt more than drips?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:11.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I've done it this time.\N--Vroom... Zoom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:14.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I must have been stressed out.\N--Zoom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:18.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I need to hurry back and start writing again.\N--Vroom-Vroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:21.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Zoom...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:24.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Vroom! Vroom-Vroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Put your mini-car on hold, and listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, here it is. Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:32.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--We came to see you.\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You girls came to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We have school today, and our school is close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You just stopped by on your way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:48.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that makes a difference, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! The drip is almost empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:57.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't someone going to come and replace it when it's empty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya expect from this low-tech place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:01.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, press the "Nurse Call"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:04.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nurse...? There's no "Nurse" here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:07.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Nurse? "Nurse"? "Nurse"...?!\N--We have to hurry and call Iku-{\i1}nee,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:10.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,or else air is going to get into Sensei's arm and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no "Nurse" in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No way?! It should be near the "pillow"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:17.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Pillow talk? "Pillow talk"...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:21.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?! Sensei's out cold! He's a mental wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:28.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The newer ones stop air from being let in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:30.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already sick, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:38.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei? Looks like your fever is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want a suppository to get the fever down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Anal medicine!\N--Anal medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you react too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:47.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No! I sternly refuse such masochistic pleasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:52.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Masochistic pleasures...\NThis is a medical practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:55.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I had one when I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:16:00.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was so embarrassed that... I puked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:03.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Too much information...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:05.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's keep an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:09.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You girls, don't strain him too much, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay.\N--Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:14.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha doing over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come out. You're going to get your clothes dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:22.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:24.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can press it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:26.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm gonna press the "Nurse"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:30.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, the drip is full now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:32.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is going to happen for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:35.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But... there are ghosts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Ghosts...?\N--Ghosts...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:41.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa told me... that there are ghosts in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're scarier than monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno what they're like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:49.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's scared too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:52.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...I wanna see one myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's gotta be made up by Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:00.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:05.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do if I can't sleep after hearing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:08.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This hospital is old, so it's really scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why not just do that anal medicine thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's there to freak about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:18.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup? I brought your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the calligraphy tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Request denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:27.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! I was waiting to get my hands on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:30.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're here 'cause you're overworked, right? So just rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:33.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm at peace when I'm working!\N--Tch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you an idiot?! Can't you tell I'm worried?!\N--What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, yeah?!\N--You look agitated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:41.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:55.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did I surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:03.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the room next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:06.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite lively, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Was it noisy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:19.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really bad. Just a summer cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:22.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, it isn't "just" a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:26.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone came by worried about you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:31.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Those are kids who were happy to see you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:37.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do get well soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.65,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Pulse"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:59.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-{\i1}san{\i0}?! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:02.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please let the Village Leader know that I want my calligraphy tools!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your fever hasn't gone down yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:09.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just came up with an idea! I can write now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:12.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please let me write! Now, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--No...\N--I need to write now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:16.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop, Sensei!\N--Every moment counts in calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:20.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't, Sensei! I have a husband...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:24.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:27.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to let you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:30.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,His fever went up with excitement...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...so I'll give him a suppository and let him sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! You okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:43.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, better than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:46.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's super!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You really got your complexion back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:52.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Must be because of the butt medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:55.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you take your prescription.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:57.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:20:00.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't test my love of my husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:05.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now, time to hurry back and start writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you look ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:11.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa from next door cheered me up yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's in this room over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:22.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Where's the elderly man in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:23.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Elderly...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:27.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you were the only one hospitalized here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:30.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the patients stay in the newer facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:36.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei? Did you see a ghost or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:15.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:17.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you potato stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:21.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your fingers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:25.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No! Nothing! These are nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:26.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:29.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha want me to do with...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:31.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...the bloody onions Sensei chopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:34.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not blood! It's spice! Hot sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:37.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The red comes from stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:39.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:43.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of get what you mean now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:46.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be bringing food again starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:47.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:50.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Sensei?
